disableFocusOnHover.description: If true, the menu item won't receive focus when the mouse moves over it.

focusVisible.description: If true, the component is being focused using keyboard.

getRootProps.description: Resolver for the root slot's props.

highlighted.description: If true, the component is being highlighted.

index.description: 0-based index of the item in the menu.

rootRef.description: The ref to the component's root DOM element.

totalItemCount.description: Total number of items in the menu.
